iv class=\"wr-exclusion-item\">Products with missing or altered service tags or serial numbers</div>\n          <div class=\"wr-exclusion-item\">Products for which we have not received payment</div>\n          <div class=\"wr-exclusion-item\">Normal degradation in aesthetics over time</div>\n          <div class=\"wr-exclusion-item\">Demo units purchased from a distributor or dealer</div>\n          <div class=\"wr-exclusion-item\">Return shipping costs to us and back to the customer</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
