 are no model exclusions for trade-in.</p>\n          <h4>Cost Formula</h4>\n          <p>Total Amount = New Model MSRP \u2212 (Trade-in Unit MSRP \u00d7 30%). The new model MSRP must be greater than the trade-in unit MSRP. No downgrades are permitted.</p>\n          <h4>Additional Options</h4>\n          <p>Faceplate inserts, artwork, engravings, and other custom options are charged at the same rate as new CIEM orders.</p>\n          <h4>Defective Units &amp; Warranty</h4>\n          <p>Defective products can be submitted for trade-in and will be treated with no difference. The new CIEM or UIEM will enjoy the full standard warranty.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</div>",
